analyses.name: AEON: main effect (0th order)

The last column reports the probability (expressed as a percentage) of these voxels being located in the respective Brodmann area (BA) or specific location (Loc) according to the cytoarchitectonic maps. ext = extension (number of voxels in a cluster); T = T-value at the voxel level. x, y, z are peak coordinates in MNI space (mm).
